{"tid":1755322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開定聖誕黃色攻略","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T16:03:06.000Z","uid":243537,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7bf092812563887978ed30a8cf069aa5b76dcdea","tid":1755322,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"多謝各位手足  我地區選贏左第一步 <br />\n但係我地唔應該停 更加唔可以停<br />\n和理非既大家要準備定錢過聖誕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好簡單2種 <br />\n網購就全球好多自由國家可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係18區黃店要大大力懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要所有黃店聖誕忙到冇得陪女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍店可以送聖誕禮物俾烏蠅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非兄弟姐妹  票贏左之後唔好完呀<br />\n仲有好多野可以做  兄弟爬山 !!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家留定18 區 各黃店 資料 <br />\n做定聖誕攻略<br />\n<br />\n各位區議員都可以做定聖誕導賞團資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16f818bd37ff083e6fb8c905eba44b15d642409","tid":1755322,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7f397df708178c45b3af97d58609c434a35d971","tid":1755322,"uid":108913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79f61f11a3c9e30f97f234282f3582f4d8267a53","ti